Description: Desktop email client with IMAP, JMAP and Microsoft 365 support
 Chithi is a desktop email client built with Tauri v2 (Rust) and Vue 3
 (TypeScript). It supports IMAP, JMAP, CalDAV, and JMAP Calendar with a
 Thunderbird-style three-pane layout.
